items.name: Gerudo Women (Legend of Zelda)
items.description:
A lora to generate your own Gerudo characters from Legend of Zelda. Trained to draw women, I haven't tried generating men. I tried my best, but this lora is a little fussy. Keep reading for some usage tips.

Trigger word is "gerudo". I also highly suggest adding "big nose" so you're more likely to get that lovely Gerudo facial structure.

It seems like I couldn't get it to pick up the colorful lips, so you have to mess around with prompts to add them yourself. What I've been doing is adding "green lips" as a prompt, and then "green face" and "green skin" as negative prompts at 1.1 weight to cancel out the weird green glow you get over the face.

If you generate some good pictures, please post them! I'm excited to see what people make.

items.name: Zeta (Batman Beyond)
items.description:
This is kind of a "deep cut" but, for those who can appreciate it, here is a lora of the boomerang faced Zeta as he appeared originally in the Kids WB show Batman Beyond during the second golden age of animation.

Notes:

Trained on NIA, intended for use with anime models. Use "zeta, robot" or "zeta, humanoid robot" to trigger him, "zeta" by itself will produce weird results. Should produce the likeness of Zeta 90% of the time. Incoherence dramatically increases the wider you make the picture. Making the image taller is a crapshoot, his spoiler boomerang head thing seems to lose its smoothness the taller you go. Denoising values for upscaling should be well below 0.4 in the 2.7 range.

As far as variability/versatility, your mileage will vary, I find it difficult to get him into different poses other than simply standing and looking intimidating. Using controlnet to pose him introduces issues with his spoiler since that is interpreted by the nn as a face.

Future:

If I can get a hold of the original episode, I could extract some high quality screen caps with a wider variety of poses to give the lora some more versatility. We'll see.

items.name: BlushySpicy - Artist Style (LoRA/Lycoris)
items.description:
If you enjoyed this model, why don't you check out my other works? I put a lot of effort into correctly recreating artist styles and making the occasional character LoRA.😊

This model was trained using the collab/guide by holostrawberry [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free - colabs | Stable Diffusion Other | Civitai

About the artist:

Twitter: Blushy&Spicy 💖🔥 (@BlushySpicy) / Twitter

Patreon: Blushy & Spicy | Creating Pinups and Fun Content! | Patreon

Blushy & Spicy make cute💖 and the occassional nsfw 🔥 images. This model works for both. Pinups in particular are some of their main creations and therefore work well in this model.

Weights & Prompts

The activation prompt is: 

blushyspicy

LoCon:

Most anime models are based on NAI. For those this should be your goto version.

Use a weight of 1.0, adjust to taste. Check the example XYZ plot for reference.

This version is also closer to blushy than spicy - it is less likely to create nsfw images unprompted.

LoRA:

Use a weight of 1.0. Go a bit lower (I used 0.9) for character loras. As usual I have included an XYZ plots for reference. Including "artist name" in the negative prompt is advised.

For backgrounds and landscapes the model is generally low on details but when prompted for explicitly it tends towards brighter colors and blurring objects out of focus. Check out the two image sets with and without the model.

Please leave a review if you enjoyed this model or have problems with it. I'd also be interested in how the model behaves with other base checkpoints, so why don't you give it a try and throw some images down below! 👇

items.name: 当代华人 Contemporary Chinese for XL & SD1.5
items.description:
尝试优化基础模型中缺乏华人形象的问题，使用 500 张人物环境肖像照，典型职业肖像照和环境照训练，力图覆盖不同性别和年龄段。

使用时无需 Trigger Words，在 SD 1.5 下权重一般不超过 0.8，在 SDXL 1.0 下权重可提高到 1.0。

注意：easynegative 和 ng_deepnegative_v1_75t 两个 Embeddings 会影响此 LoRA 效果，请避免同时使用。

V2.0 for SDXL 1.0 更新：

SDXL 1.0 对亚洲人形象的支持，相对于 SD 1.5 已经有了很大的提升。 我仍然针对 SDXL 训练了一个版本，在基础模型表现不佳的情况下可以尝试使用此 LoRA。

以下的说明主要针对 SD 1.5 版本。

V2.0 for SD 1.5 更新：

  1. 以 fp16 精度保存，以提供对早期显卡的支持。

  2. 基于 Realistic Vision v2.0 训练，大幅提高 epochs 到 80，大幅提高了人物形象和场景的真实性。

  3. 由于真实性的提高，可能在一些情况下，美学效果有所降低。如需要可继续使用 V1.2 版。

以下是基于 Realistic Vision v2.0 进行的 4 组对比，展示基础模型原生亚洲人（Asian），华人（Chinese）与本 LoRA 在权重 0.8 下生成的华人形象的区别：




此 LoRA 可与主要的基础模型配合使用。以下是基于 5 个常用基础模型（Realistic Vision v4.0，ReV Animated v1.2.2，Deliberate v2，ChilloutMix，Disney Pixar Cartoon type B v1.0）的应用效果对比：

items.name: Tangbohu foreground ??? Blur LoRA (唐伯虎前景???模糊LoRA)
items.description:
This is a LoRA used to control foreground blur while maintaining the original image as much as possible;

Reducing the weight will gradually blur the foreground, with a maximum/minimum of -5! More upper limits can be explored.

When using larger weights, there may be significant changes in the image

This is a demand for Laotie to ask questions, which is a bit strange. The effect is similar to that of taking photos without focusing on the top, and the final effect is not particularly ideal. In order to stabilize the background and not be blurred together, I added the background fuzzy control lora I made on some samples to make the background clear. For entertainment only, don't take it seriously.

这是一个LoRA，用于控制前景模糊，同时尽量保持原图；

减少权重会使前景逐渐模糊，最高/最低可达-5！更多的上限可以探索下。

使用较大权重的时候画面有可能会产生比较大的变化

这是一个老铁提问的需求，有点太奇怪了，效果类似拍照片没有对焦对上的感觉，最终的效果不是特别理想，为了稳定背景不会被一起模糊掉，我又在部分样图上加入了我制作的背景模糊控制lora来使背景清晰。仅供娱乐，不要当真。

これは、元の図をできるだけ維持しながら、前景のぼやけを制御するLoRAです。

重みを減らすと、将来性が徐々にぼやけて、最高/最低-5になります！より多くの上限を探索することができる。

大きな重みを使うと画面が大きく変化する可能性があります

これは1つの古い鉄の質問の需要で、少し怪しすぎて、効果は似ていて写真を撮ってピントが合っていない感じがして、最終的な効果は特に理想的ではありません、背景が一緒にぼやけないように安定するために、私はまた一部のサンプルに私が作った背景のぼやけ制御ローラを加えて背景をはっきりさせます。娯楽だけを提供して、真に受けるな。

此ckpt魔改的来源是用户大江户战士的线稿lora。最开始魔改的目标是为了让角色lora也轻松能产生线稿(不过目前看来更适合画风lora)

使用画师lora和角色lora均能产生线稿关键词和用户大江户战士的线稿lora一样,需要有lineart, monochrome.使用时不要使用有关颜色的提示词，但是请注意，提示词中没有颜色不代表lora本身不会有颜色表现，根据lora本身的各种提示词权重和可能的过拟合状态也可能会出现颜色表现。不过反过来想可以通过写上颜色只让某些地方上色

Both artist's Lora and character Lora can generate lineart, monochrome. The keywords for generating sketches are the same as those used for CyberAIchemist's Anime Lineart Lora, which include "lineart" and "monochrome". Do not use color-related prompt when generating the sketches. However, please note that the absence of color-related prompt does not necessarily mean that Lora itself will not have color expressions. Depending on the weight of various prompt of Lora itself and the possible overfitting state, color expressions may also occur.Thinking the other way around, it is possible to selectively color only certain parts of the sketch by specifying color only in those parts.

items.name: Korean Sumukhwa Model ver 1
items.description:
I updated the model's name to be more accurate. As I am not a native English speaker, it is hard for me to understand the nuances of the title, so I changed it to prevent misunderstandings.

By the way, I used ChatGPT to translate this message.

이전에 제작했던 하이퍼넷트워크에 이어서 이번엔 파인튜닝 한 나온 모델을 공유합니다. 그리고 모델 사용 가이드로 남깁니다. 데이터는 공유마당에 있는 김홍도 그림 중 선별 한 자료와 Ai허브에 올라와 있는 한국화 데이터셋 입니다.

Continuing from the previous Hypernetworks, I am sharing the fine-tuned model and providing a guide for its usage. The data used for training includes selected materials from Kim Hong-do's paintings available on the Gongu Sharing Market and the Korean painting dataset on AI Hub.

허깅페이스 모델 주소

HuggingFace model address

https://huggingface.co/gagong/korean-sumukhwa-model-ver-1

모델에 사용된 자료 출처

Sources of the data used in the model

  • 공유마당 https://gongu.copyright.or.kr/gongu/search/search/list.do?viewType=&collection=gongu_wrt&kwd=%EA%B9%80%ED%99%8D%EB%8F%84&

  • Ai허브 https://www.aihub.or.kr/aihubdata/data/view.do?currMenu=115&topMenu=100&aihubDataSe=realm&dataSetSn=71380

학습과정

Training Process

이미지를 768×768사이즈로 바꾼뒤, clip_interrogator를 통해 프롬프트를 만들었습니다. 이후 한국 수묵화 자료에 gksrnrghk라는 프롬프트를 붙이고, 김홍도 그림에는 rlaghdeh라는 프롬프트를 추가로 붙였습니다. 이 이미지를 다시 512×512사이즈로 바꾼 뒤 Stable Tuner를 이용해서 학습을 했습니다. 사용한 설정은 아래와 같습니다.

The images were resized to 768×768, and prompts were created using the clip_interrogator. The prompt "gksrnrghk" was added for Korean ink wash painting data, and an additional prompt "rlaghdeh" was added for Kim Hong-do's paintings. These images were then resized to 512×512, and training was performed using the Stable Tuner. The following settings were used

  • pretrained model: runwayml/stable-diffusion-v1-5

  • seed: 3434554

  • resolution: 512

  • train batch size: 24

  • num train epochs: 60

  • learning rate: 5e-6

원래 768 모델을 생각하고 제작했으나, 실행할 수 있는 환경이 제약이 크고 컨트롤넷을 사용할 수 없었기에 512모델 1.5버전으로 다시 작업을 했습니다.

Originally, I intended to create a 768 model, but due to constraints on the execution environment and the unavailability of the Controlnet, I had to work with the 512 model version 1.5.

자료가 이미 준비 되어있기 때문에 경우에 따라서는 (예산이라든지) 새롭게 학습 할 지도 모르겠습니다.

Since the data is already prepared, it may not be necessary to train again in some cases (e.g., budget constraints).

사용 가이드

Usage Guide

한국 수묵화 데이터는 6000장 정도 김홍도 그림은 1000장 정도 사용되었습니다. 그런 이유인지, 한국 수묵화 스타일로 하려면 CFG Scale를 2-7 사이로 김홍도 그림의 스타일로 하려면 4-12사이를 추천합니다. 두개의 스타일 모두 활용할 경우 중간 값으로 하는 것을 추천합니다. 스텝수에도 영향을 받기 때문에 적절한 값을 찾는 것이 중요합니다.

For Korean ink wash painting style, it is recommended to use CFG Scale between 2-7. For Kim Hong-do's painting style, a range of 4-12 is recommended. If you want to utilize both styles, it is recommended to use an intermediate value. The step count also affects the output, so finding an appropriate value is important.

작동을 잘 하지않지만 기법에 대한 프롬프트도 적용이 되어있으며 사용할 때는 아래 프롬프트를 사용하면 됩니다. (하지만 미묘한 차이만이 발생합니다.)

Although it does not perform well, the prompts for the techniques are applied, and when using it, you can use the following prompts. (However, only subtle differences may occur.) Translate it into English.

  • 백묵법/Baekmukbeob: baegmyobeob

  • 몰골법/molgolbeob: molgolbeob

  • 구륵법/guleugbeob: guleugbeob

김홍도 그림을 강조하고 싶으면 rlaghdeh style, rlaghdeh painting이란 프롬프트를 같이 사용하면 좀더 강조가 됩니다.

If you want to emphasize Kim Hong-do's painting style, using the prompts "rlaghdeh style" and "rlaghdeh painting" together will enhance the emphasis.

샘플 이미지

Sample Images

txt2img의 샘플이미지 입니다.

Here is a sample image from txt2img


gksrnrghk, sky, tree Steps: 40, Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras, CFG scale: 2.0, Seed: 1271864954, Size: 768×512, Model hash: a710c70889, Model: gksrnrghk_15_512_60, Clip skip: 2, Script: X/Y/Z plot, X Type: Prompt S/R, X Values: “gksrnrghk,\”gksrnrghk, rlaghdeh\”,rlaghdeh “, Y Type: CFG Scale, Y Values: “2,3,4,5,7,9,12,15”, Version: v1.3.0

한국화의 경우 높은 CFG에서 흑백이 아닌 컬러가 나오기 시작합니다.

In the case of Korean ink wash painting, colors start to appear at higher CFG values instead of black and white.

v3.0 - General improvement & flexibility. Well, SDXL LoRA's are massive both in training time and size, so i decided to improve my older models instead.

v2.0 - Improved face generation, overall more closer to geralt's likeness than v1.0 Increased dataset and training steps. Trimmed some extra keywords. I'll most likely make a lora for Regis next.

Main Trigger Word - geralt_soul3142 , check examples for other ones.

RECOMMENDATIONS :-

Use LoRA name according to the downloaded file when copying example prompts.

  1. Highres Fix : Use if you are getting blurry and ugly images & try reducing LoRA weight

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  2. Weight: 0.5 - 0.8

  3. Clip Skip: 2

  4. Denoising : Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

  5. For better face's : use ADetailer

There are imperfections here & there, which i usually leave it in as is, (i never do any inpainting in examples), most of which like hands can be fixed with better prompting, negative embeddings while other like weapons are just bad majority of the time no matter the model as of today.

Some LoRA's are flexible with any clothing, some are not so keep these things in mind.

This is an unofficial fanmade LoRA, not intended for any commercial purpose and use. All characters and IP rights are owned by their respective creators and owners. I do not own rights to any of these characters.

items.name: LoRA GDM Modern Interior Design - Luxury 8K
items.description:
This is the ultimate LORA for Luxury Modern Interior Design trained on the style of GDM with 8k steps, 260 images (captioned and tokened). This LoRA is designed to be flexible and mixed into prompts instead of having a dedicated checkpoint. Has been thoroughly tested to find the best Steps/CFG/Weight/Training Combination.

***Remember to adjust the weight of the LoRA as needed. Start with 1 weight and go lower as needed, if you see artifacts/issues. I found the weight can go down to 0.30 and work well.***

RECOMMENDED SETTINGS SD 1.5:

Steps: 70 (Between 60-80)

CFG: 9.5 (Between 7.5-11.5)

Prompt Trigger Words: " <lora:gdmintlora:1> luxury modern interior design, xxxx room "

Replace the "xxxx" with living room, dining, bath, bed etc.

Tip#1: Try to use the above Steps and CFG settings first and tweak from there. I think 60 steps may be the minimum acceptable quality. CFG 7.5 is minimum and after 11.5, will be a hit or a miss. But you can try other settings to fit your needs.

大家好，我是chosen鲷

中国著名武侠小说作者金庸老先生对于它笔下的独孤求败有这样一段描写“独孤求败的最后一把剑为木剑，在其剑冢下刻字，四十岁后，不滞于物，草木竹石均可为剑。自此精修，渐进于无剑胜有剑之境。”

我在测试这个lora的时候，突然闪回了上面那段剧情，因为我在测试lora的时候有个习惯，我会先不输入任何tag，只打上很简单的质量词和LORA的提示词，然后看看效果，而这个模型，恰恰就在这种情况下，能做出最为令人惊叹的画面来，是的，你没看错，我这些例图里面都没有tag，我没有输入任何一个tag，在这一瞬间，我也悟道了，我感觉我仿佛能窥探到AI绘画的终极形态了，一切的tag只不过是在禁锢AI罢了，这个东西的终极形态将会是，选择合适的模型，合适的lora，然后不需要任何的tag了，让它自由的去发挥创造吧，我想这可能正是金庸老先生所说的“无剑胜有剑之境”吧

items.name: Notice of Hiatus

Notice of Hiatus

Dear model makers and lovers,

Since I started playing around with SD in February, I have met many amazing people and have done many amazing things I would never have thought possible before. We really do live in exciting times, and I feel privileged to be able to share these moments with you. Thank you, I love you all very much!

Unfortunately, I must tell you that I intend to take a break in order to focus on myself, gather inspiration, and travel. I have been so laser-focused on AI creation these past months that I might have lost touch with the beauty of the real world which is unhealthy in my opinion.

I do intend to come back at a later date in the future, refreshed, and able to deliver you all fresh, original, high quality EDG-grade content. In the meantime, please do keep my content alive, like the models you haven't liked yet, and review the models you haven't reviewed yet.

Take care, have fun!

Best,

EDG

items.name: Alexia - Hentai University
items.description:
This is a LoRA for the character Alexia, from Hentai University a game by Noodle Jacuzzi.

Alexia's art is from the artist Oreteki18kin, the set -

Futaba-chan Jusei Chu☆

I've been working my way through making these for all the characters currently in the game, and sharing them in the Discord for HU, but figured I should also put them up here.

In general, I'm working from pretty limited image sets, so expect the results to be a bit wonky at times.

I recommend a weight of around 0.5, possibly lower depending if you're combining the character LoRA with other styles/costumes/etc. along with tagging some defining characteristics of the character you're generating. Higher than that can really push the artist's original style, and may cause you issues.

All characters I train have a "character tag" added into the set to help generate them fairly reliably.

Recommended LoRA Weight - 0.5 for fairly flexible, higher if you want more of the original artist's style, lower if it doesn't play nice with other loras.

Character tag - HUAlexia
Recommended tags - brown hair, short hair, brown eyes, large breasts,

I may have forgotten to check and tag eye color when doing my testing, but hey. If you want it to be "set accurate" be sure to tag. Also, huge or large, take your pick on how "endowed" she should be.

I've got quite a backlog of these made up already, so I'll be uploading them on and off.

Check my other uploads as I put them out for more HU characters, and if you want any specific character put up soon, let me know.
